
@startuml

' Define classes
class User {
    - username: String (unique)
    - password: String
}

class Player {
    + playGame(game: Game): void
    + pauseGame(): void
    + resumeGame(): void
}

class Admin {
    + createGame(): Game
    + designGame(game: Game): void
    + publishGame(game: Game): void
}

class Game {
    - name: String (unique)
    - admin: Admin
    - hallOfFame: HallOfFame
    - blocks: List<Block>
    - levels: List<Level>
    - minSpeed: int
    - speedIncreaseFactor: float
    - maxLength: int
    - minLength: int
}

class HallOfFame {
    - scores: Map<Player, int>
}

class Block {
    - color: Color
    - points: int (1-1000)
}

class Level {
    - number: int (1-99)
    - gridLayout: GridLayout
    - isRandom: boolean
    - initialBlocksCount: int
}

class GridLayout {
    - grid: 2DArray<BlockPosition>
}

class BlockPosition {
    - x: int
    - y: int
    - block: Block
}

class Paddle {
    - length: int
    - position: int
}

class Ball {
    - position: Point
    - direction: Direction
    - speed: int
}

class GameSession {
    - player: Player
    - game: Game
    - currentLevel: Level
    - lives: int = 3
    - score: int
    - isPaused: boolean
    + startGame(): void
    + endGame(): void
    + nextLevel(): void
    + loseLife(): void
    + updateScore(points: int): void
}

class Point {
    - x: int
    - y: int
}

class Direction {
    - dx: int
    - dy: int
}

class Color {
    - name: String
}

' Relationships
User <|-- Player
User <|-- Admin
Admin "1" --> "1" Game : designs
Game "1" --> "1" HallOfFame
Game "1" --> "n" Block : contains
Game "1" --> "n" Level : has
Player "n" --> "n" Game : plays
GameSession "1" --> "1" Player
GameSession "1" --> "1" Game
GameSession "1" --> "1" Level : currentLevel
Game "1" --> "1" Admin : admin
Level "1" --> "1" GridLayout
GridLayout "1" --> "n" BlockPosition
BlockPosition "1" --> "1" Block
GameSession "1" --> "1" Paddle
GameSession "1" --> "1" Ball
Ball "1" --> "1" Direction
Ball "1" --> "1" Point : position
Paddle "1" --> "1" Point : position

@enduml

---

### Notes:

- The `User` class serves as a base class for both `Player` and `Admin`.
- Each `Game` is associated with one `Admin`, but a user can be an admin in one game and a player in another.
- A `Game` has multiple `Level`s, each with its own `GridLayout`.
- `BlockPosition` represents the position of a block within the grid.
- `GameSession` tracks the state of a player’s current or paused game session.
- The `HallOfFame` maintains the top scores for each `Player` in a given `Game`.

